
README for Cal3D
================

Name:                   Cal3D
License:                LGPL
Maintainer:             Dirk Reiners <dirk@opensg.org>
Initial Author:         Dirk Reiners <dirk@opensg.org>
Additional Libraries:   cal3d
Added:                  2005/09/11
Last modified:          2005/09/11
Last tested:            2005/09/11

Description:

A wrapper for the Cal3D character animatiom system (cal3d.sf.net).

This has not been tested in a multi-thread environment and it probably 
won't work there. Be warned!


WARNING: the hardware skinning shader trigger a bug on nVidia drivers and
don't work, ignore for now!

Yours

    Dirk
    
